snippet.title: Lifecraft Teaser - Intracellular Gameplay
snippet.description:
Website: https://lifecraft.life/
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/TwsNSCHaN8
Join us on Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/lifecraft/

Lifecraft teaser showcasing intracellular gameplay composed of proteine synthesis and assembling, load and unload of materials into vessels, catalysis of reactions, production of energy and even some cellular growth thanks to dispatchers.

Everything is recorded directly with the latest alpha build, so it's the actual engine, but the gameplay itself is still under heavy development. Consider this just a taste of what the first layer of gameplay will be!
